txt.en: The lumbering troll is defeated, but you are alarmed to find dangerous creatures becoming even more threatening upon contracting this mysterious disease.  You have a feeling further horrors await you deeper in Agarnaith.
TBD Go to Agarnaith Ranger Camp
While scouting the wilds of Agarnaith, you stumble upon a diseased troll.

While scouting the wilds of Agarnaith, you stumble upon a diseased troll. You decide that it is for the best to prevent this dangerous beast from harming others before continuing your soggy journey through thorn and thicket.
Infected trolls can be found in the wilds of Agarnaith.\n\nYou should defeat infected trolls.
